==English==

===Noun===
'''satisfaction'''

# [[fulfillment]] of a [[need]] or [[desire]].
# the [[pleasure]] obtained by such fulfillment.
# the [[source]] of such [[gratification]].
# [[reparation]] for an [[injury]] or [[loss]].
# [[vindication]] for a [[wrong]] [[suffered]].

